sequenceDiagram
    participant Op as Operator
    participant CLI as virmux research
    participant Srv as internal/skill/research
    participant FS as runs/<id>/
    participant DB as SQLite (runs/virmux.sqlite)

    Op->>CLI: research run --query "..."
    CLI->>Srv: Planner.Compile(query)
    Srv->>FS: persist plan.yaml
    CLI->>DB: research.plan.created
    CLI->>Srv: Scheduler.Run(plan)
    par Tracks
        Srv->>Srv: Mapper.Exec(track)
        Srv->>FS: map/<id>.jsonl
        Srv->>DB: evidence rows
    end
    CLI->>Srv: Reducer.Synthesize(maps)
    Srv->>FS: reduce/report.md
    CLI->>Op: JSON Summary
